biography:
### Main Activities
- Physics at the [University of Turin (UniTO)](https://www.unito.it);
- Mathematical, statistical and computational modelling of complex systems at the [Interdisciplinary Physics Team (InPhyT)](https://github.com/InPhyT);
- Developing FOSS at [InPhyT](https://github.com/InPhyT), [UniTO-SEPI](https://github.com/UniTo-SEPI), [JuliaEpi](https://github.com/JuliaEpi), [JuliaHealth](https://github.com/JuliaHealth), [JuliaGraphs](https://github.com/JuliaGraphs);
- Working on NeuronalModelling.jl: a flexible and high-performance computational framework for the specification, calibration and simulation of quantitative single-neuron models;
- Learning about automated theorem provers and interactive proof assistants to formalise, digitise and verify mathematical assertions.

